line: King Ragnar: Welcome.
My name is Ragnar Lothbrok.
I am the King of Sweden.
You are the warrior Leif.
Do you know why I summoned you?
Leif: I do not.
Ragnar: The Seeress told me that the gods favour you.
I intend to test this theory. I have a task for you.
There is a clan just north of here.
They are small but powerful.
If the gods truly protect you, eliminate this clan.
If you succeed I will bring you to raid England with me.
Leif: I will not fail you King Ragnar!
Leif:  I have been given a great task my friends.
Astrid:  What is it?
Knut:  Yes, tell us!
Leif: He is sending me to raid a clan up north.
If I succeed he will take me to find England with him.
Astrid: What? An entire clan by yourself??
Knut: Go ahead and get yourself killed.
Astrid: Knut!
Knut: He will never survive on his own.
Am I wrong?
Astrid: Leif is a mighty warrior!
Leif: Ragnar Lothbrok himself told me that the gods protect me.
They will ensure my success!
Astrid: This is amazing news Leif!
Knut: Haha. He is lying to you.
He is sending you to your death.
Leif: Ragnar Lothbrok would not do that!
Astrid: Be careful with your words Knut.
Knut: I am merely making an observation.
Leif: Enough of this. I am going to conquer this clan!
Leif: Odin gives me victory this day!
Knut: You succeeded all on your own? How?
Astrid: He already told you Knut.
Knut: That's impossible!
Leif: I must find King Ragnar.
King Ragnar: It seems you were successful.
The seeress was correct.
I expected as much.
Leif: Ragnar will you allow me to join you on your next raid?
King Ragnar: I will bring you if you swear to be loyal to me.
Leif: I swear King Ragnar.
King Ragnar: Bring your friends too. What are their names?
Leif: Astrid and Knut.
King Ragnar: Yes. They will be useful on the raid.
I will tell them that they are coming.
Now go ready yourself to set sail. We leave soon.
King Ragnar: I see land!
There it is....
England!
We will find many treasures here my friends.
Leif: The gods have guided us to find this new land.
Astrid: The gods are with us as long as we follow King Ragnar.
Knut: ....
King Ragnar: It is time to raid!!!
King Ragnar: Odin has granted us victory!!
Astrid: The gods show favour to King Ragnar.
King Ragnar: We are not finished yet.
I have heard of a place nearby with great goods to plunder.
We attack tonight!
King Ragnar: Another victory!
Surely this is proof that Odin approves of our conquests
Leif: We have amassed great wealth here.
Perhaps it is time to return home my King.
Knut: We should attack every saxon in this pitiful land!
King Ragnar: We have one more monastery to raid.
Then perhaps we shall leave for now.
Astrid: I long to return home.
Knut: Urgh..
Astrid: I can't wait to return to Sweden.
King Ragnar: The gods guide us on our journey home.
Knut: The gods cant help you Ragnar....
I've arranged a surprise for you when we return hehehe.
King Ragnar: Impossible!
Why would anyone attack me in my own land.
I fear I have been betrayed.
Leif I need your help in taking back my lands.
Leif: I will help you Ragnar.
King Ragnar: Thank you my friend
King Ragnar: You never cease to amaze me Leif.
I feel you are the only one I can trust
Leif: I am loyal to you Ragnar.
King Ragnar: What about your friends?
Leif: I trust them with my life.
King Ragnar: Then I trust them too.
Come. We must finish liberating my lands from these invaders.
King Ragnar: My lands are free.
I have plans to avenge the people we lost.
Leif: How can we avenge them?
Knut: I think we should just forget about it.
There is no use worrying about spoiled apples.
Astrid: What?
Knut: Nevermind. We should move on.
King Ragnar: I cannot move on.
We will sail around Scandinavia.
We will destroy this clan and find out who betrayed me.
Leif: I am with you Ragnar.
Leif: There is the clan.
we should attack them at night!
King Ragnar: We are not finished.
We shall raid every village that belonged to them.
I will find out who betrayed me.
Knut: Hmpfh... Im sure we will find them.
Knut: We should stop searching for the betrayer.
King Ragnar: Argh.
Perhaps you are right.
We must return home.
King Ragnar: I have a plan my friends.
We are going to raid the city of Paris.
It is a large and powerful city but together we shall conquer it.
Leif: How will we do this Ragnar?
King Ragnar: Together. They can not stop all of us.
Astrid: We stand with you Ragnar.
Knut: Yes....
Leif: I am ready to fight.
King Ragnar: There it is. Paris.
We should attack some of the forts nearby first.
King Ragnar: We control part of the land around Paris.
Knut: We should attack the city now.
They cannot stop us.
Leif: We need to cut off their supply first.
King Ragnar: Leif is right.
We attack the supply routes.
King Ragnar: We are ready.
Paris is ours for the taking.
Odin is with us!
Follow me and take this city.
King Ragnar: Paris is ours!
Leif: Odin has granted us victory.
Astrid: The gods truly are with you King Ragnar.
King Ragnar: Indeed. They are also with Leif.
I could not do this without you my friend.
Knut: .....
King Ragnar: We don't have much time to celebrate.
The Franks will return soon to try take back the city.
Prepare yourselves for the next assault.
King Ragnar: It is time to leave.
We shall not return to Sweden.
Odin wants me to go to England. I can feel it.
King Ragnar: I know my destiny lies in England.
Leif: What awaits us?
King Ragnar: You shall see soon.
Knut: Hehehe. It will be your end.
King Ragnar: This is the place.
It is beautiful.
I can feel the gods here.
Leif: What is that noise?
Ragnar wait!!
* Falls through trap door plunging into snake pit *
Leif: RAGNAR NOOOO!
It is a Saxon trap!
How did they know we were coming?
Astrid: We must have been betrayed again.
This time it cost us the life of King Ragnar.
Knut: No way of ever knowing so just forget about it.
Odin: Enough of these foolish games Loki!
Knut: Arrgh! What are you doing here?
Leif: Wait are you?....
Odin: Yes Leif. I am Odin.
Ragnar has been murdered. By your friend Knut.
However, that is not really his name.
Knut is actually the trickster Loki in disguise.
Your games have gone too far Loki!!
Astrid: I am not Astrid. I am the goddess Freya.
* Removes disguise *
Freya: I joined you to guide you.
I also wanted to try to save Ragnar from Loki.
I am sorry I could not save you Ragnar.
Knut: Hehehe. I wondered if he would ever realise.
* Removes disguise *
Loki: Now bow before me Leif, You fool.
Odin: No Loki. I will punish you for your crimes.
Loki: We will see about that.
* Vanishes in smoke *
Odin: Loki loves his games.
I fear he intends to destroy all of Asgard.
Leif, We will need your your help.
Leif: I would be honored to help the gods.
Odin: First you must destroy the rest of Loki's soldiers.
Odin: There are many still in England.
When you have completed this task I will take you to Asgard.
For I fear Loki's plans.
Leif: I will not fail you.
Leif: I have eliminated Loki's soldiers.
What do we do next?
Odin: We go to Asgard.
Odin: We are here. This is Asgard.
It seems we are too late. Loki's soldiers are here.
Thor: You are not too late father.
The fun has just begun.
Thor: We have beaten back Loki's goons.
Who is this one?
Leif: I am Leif. Here to help fight against Loki.
Thor: Where is Loki?
Freya: He escaped to Jotunheim.
Odin: We shall chase him there.
But first we must get to the Bifrost.
Odin: We have made it
Now we go to Jotunheim
Odin: I do not like this land.
It reminds me of death.
Thor: I'm ready for a fight!
Let's hurry after Loki.
Thor: You will pay for what you have done Loki
Loki: Lets agree to disagree.
You will never catch me!
Odin: We shall see Loki.
We shall see.
Loki: Argh!
Why wont you quit!
Leif: I will have justice for Ragnar!
Freya: You will never play tricks on us again Loki!
Odin: It is over Loki!
Loki: I think this is all just a misunderstanding.
Can't we just all move on?
* Ties up and gags Loki *
Odin: We are taking you back to Asgard to be imprisoned.
Thank you for the help Leif.
When it's your time I shall see you in the halls of Valhalla.
Freya: Goodbye Leif.
I will await you in Valhalla.
Thor: I have a feeling we will see each other again.
But for now, farewell.
